d entanglement transition based on the subsystem\nparticle-number fluctuations. This quantity should readily be measured by the\ncurrent techniques of quantum gas microscopy and is in practice easier to\nobtain than the entanglement entropy itself.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Apr 2020 19:35:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Aug 2020 10:13:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 12 Feb 2021 03:43:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-15"}
