elian anyon\nmodel can be realized as the representation category of some non-lattice\nextremal vertex operator algebra generalizing the moonshine realization of the\ntrivial anyon model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 25 Apr 2020 03:39:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 May 2020 14:37:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2020 02:23:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-30"}
